You are given a candidate for the second sentence and you need to identify if the given sentence connects the first sentence with the rest of the story. Indicate your answer by “Yes” if it connects, otherwise “No”.

 Emphasis & Caution: The given sentence is incorrect if it changes the subsequent storyline, so that at least one of the three subsequent sentences no longer work Or in other words, the incorrect sentence and the original subsequent sentences can no longer form a consistent story.
